      "author": "leotomhal",
      "description": "## 🎉 Sector Tasks 1.0.0 — first stable release\r\n\r\nThe Time Sector workflow is complete, and the part of the plugin that writes to your file is now covered by an automated test suite.\r\n\r\nHighlights across the 0.x series, now stable:\r\n- **Sector board** with fully configurable tags, Weekly/Monthly/Daily reviews, and review reminders\r\n- **Today sidebar** with overdue / due-today / due-tomorrow, a tab badge, and quick actions\r\n- **Quick capture** and **right-click due dates** without leaving your note\r\n- **Safe auto-cleanup** that archives completed tasks before removing them\r\n\r\n### This release\r\n- Added `authorUrl` to the manifest.\r\n\r\n**Full changelog:** https://github.com/leotomhal/sector-tasks-obsidian/compare/0.27.0...1.0.0",
