      "author": "leotomhal",
      "description": "## New\r\n\r\n- **Due tomorrow** section in the Today sidebar, below Overdue and Due today.\r\n- **Tab badge** on the Today sidebar showing the count of overdue + due-today tasks, so you see what needs attention even when the panel is collapsed.\r\n- **Right-click due dates:** right-click any open task row (board or Today sidebar) to set the due date to Today / Tomorrow / Next week or clear it — without opening the Tasks modal. An \"Edit in Tasks modal…\" entry is still there for the full editor.\r\n\r\n**Full changelog:** https://github.com/leotomhal/sector-tasks-obsidian/compare/0.24.0...0.25.0",
